{"tid":1625294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民意調查 出定抖？","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:53:47.000Z","uid":32922,"like":19,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98bb433ffbc0bfa39d68461da1d64af0a16b4ec4","tid":1625294,"uid":32922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:30:06.000Z","msg":"見有人話今日要休息<br />\n有d又話要繼續開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食lunch隔離枱藍絲話今日除左冇「地鐵」之外一切都幾好又和平咁樣 班曱甴無得再蒙面搞事<br />\n<br />\n學隔離post話齋 到左聽日<br />\n林鄭又可以話 禁蒙面法 成功止暴制亂 卓有成效<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以做個民意搜集？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />休你老母 革命有得抖？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係要休息一日 留力聽日啦<br />\n<br />\n無論出同唔出 都 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後     <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，反抗</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"778a032f907d83893d7e7c556d54685958bad36c","tid":1625294,"uid":32922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"自推十口 1/10"},{"pid":"7e5c44bffb9ef5fedb8d721d0961443ead0cd018","tid":1625294,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:32:11.000Z","msg":"出，但唔洗咁大力"},{"pid":"cdb9f63c1b693fcccb8a0086631de8635cc0db2c","tid":1625294,"uid":32922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:33:06.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c87052fb3a1bc63acbcc8fec9faada7efdcad07d","tid":1625294,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"要有返一次和理非行街，要吹大雞果隻"},{"pid":"847dd896271b0a33c